description: Canyon walls, smooth from rain and faded from the light, feature striated bands of color ranging from a deep rust to a pale sandstone.  The matching stripes on parallel sides of the alleyway clearly indicate this stone was once whole, though it's now separated by several lengths.  Twin rows of torches illuminate the pass, their golden light casting dancing shadows.
